                    "paragraphs":[
                        "Section 1003.2 currently provides a definition of branch office, which includes separate definitions for branches of (1) banks, savings associations, and credit unions and (2) for-profit mortgage-lending institutions (other than banks, savings associations, and credit unions). The Bureau proposed technical and nonsubstantive modifications to the definition of branch office. The Bureau received no comments on proposed \u00a7 1003.2(c) or proposed comments 2(c)-2 and -3. The Bureau is adopting \u00a7 1003.2(c) and comments 2(c)-2 and -3, renumbered as comment 2(c)(1)-2 and comment 2(c)(2)-1, with technical modifications. The Bureau is also republishing comment (Branch Office)-1, renumbered as comment 2(c)(1)-1."
